Winter Hibernation <<< Winter Astrophotography 🏔️ Celebrate the solstice by bundling up and venturing out to snap a view of the chilly night sky. 

@nikhil.outdoors photographed this incredible moment of the northern lights in Norway with his #Pixel. “This is one of the best aurora shows that I captured. The artistry gets so incredible sometimes that even the sea stays silent in awe just watching and reflecting the beauty.” 

See g.co/pixel/astrophotography to learn more.
